../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/selector.md:18:Chain 03 stays in because it preserves the strongest pressure-adjacent live lead without sliding back into the dead coefficient-shrinkage architecture. It is materially different from Chain 02: the unit of attack is not Fourier triads but the full stretching mechanism `S omega . omega` together with pressure-Hessian debt. It is also likely to produce a calibrated obstruction even if it does not promote to proposition scale, which makes it a strong third slot.
