../../../../runtime/logs/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-step-008-explorer-001-rerun.log:1383:Chain 03 is serious and well-disciplined after refinement, but it has the weakest combined profile of the finalists. Its overlap risk is high, its positive route is less clearly differentiated from existing tensor/alignment families, and its likely success mode is an obstruction memo with a lower novelty ceiling than the helical route and a lower theorem-shaped ceiling than Chain 01.
