+
+## Output Requirements
+
+Write:
+
+- `REPORT.md`
+- `REPORT-SUMMARY.md`
+
+Keep the result overlap-first and endpoint-bound. The goal is to decide what
+family menu is real, not to rescue the branch rhetorically.
