+- `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/pressure-tensor-identity-remains-only-a-narrow-testable-possibility.md`
+- `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/real-progress-requires-a-smaller-effective-coefficient.md`
+- `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/same-scale-exterior-or-harmonic-remainder-is-immediate-failure-on-the-full-pairing.md`
+- `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/tao-sensitivity-is-only-an-admission-screen-unless-the-full-pairing-coefficient-shrinks.md`
+- `library/factual/far-field-pressure-obstruction/algebraic-rewrites-and-local-geometry-fail-the-tao-gate.md`
