+
+## Output Requirements
+
+Write:
+
+- `REPORT.md`
+- `REPORT-SUMMARY.md`
+
+Keep the result packaging-screen-first and endpoint-bound. The goal is to
+decide whether any family survives Step 10, not to freeze the later tensor
+representation.
