+# Meta Note - Step 010 Exploration 001
+
+When an endpoint-first branch has already frozen one theorem ledger and one
+gain currency, prior-art overlap screening should collapse family labels before
+any packaging work begins.
+
+Reusable lesson:
+
+- `full stretching control` can remain only a bottleneck slogan if it never
+  acquires an exact cash-out on the frozen ledger;
+- alignment, eigenframe, restricted-Euler, and conditional-regularity language
+  should be treated as overlap comparators or packaging aliases unless they
+  state estimate-level action on the same live bad term;
+- and `harmonic-moment cancellation` may be only a mechanism subquestion inside
+  a pressure-Hessian family rather than a second family.
+
+For this step, the honest family menu collapsed to one narrow
+pressure-Hessian / strain-defect line attached to the frozen `I_p^far`
+pairing, with no novelty clearance yet.
