 # History of Report Summaries
 
 Exploration summaries will be appended here as they land.
+
+---
+
+## Exploration 001
+
+# Step-010 Exploration 001 Summary
+
+- Goal:
+  map the real prior-art neighborhood for Step 10 and reduce the live
+  candidate-family menu inside the frozen `I_p^far` endpoint ledger.
+
+- What I tried:
+  read the Step-10 goal, the Step-009 freeze, the run-006 selected / judgment /
+  attack materials, the run-004 tensor-overlap critique, and the local factual
+  and meta notes governing endpoint attachment, Tao screening, and same-scale
+  harmonic failure; then compared candidate labels by closest prior family and
+  by whether they state estimate-level action on the frozen full pairing.
+
+- Outcome:
+  `succeeded`
+
+- One key takeaway:
+  the honest live menu has collapsed to one endpoint-attached
+  `pressure-Hessian / strain-defect` family, with `harmonic-moment
+  cancellation` only as a narrow mechanism subquestion; no family is yet shown
+  to survive as clearly more than repackaged prior-art language.
+
+- Reduced family menu:
+  one family only:
+  `pressure-Hessian / strain-defect`, understood strictly as a possible route
+  to smaller coefficient on the frozen full pairing `I_p^far`.
+  Collapse `pressure-tensor identity`, `harmonic-moment cancellation`, and
+  related moment-cancellation labels into this same family.
+  Reject `full stretching control` as a family label.
+  Treat alignment, eigenframe, restricted-Euler, and conditional-regularity
+  language as overlap comparators or packaging aliases, not survivors.
+
+- Leads worth pursuing:
+  test whether the pressure-tensor identity can produce packaging-independent,
+  estimate-level coefficient shrinkage on the full `I_p^far` pairing after
+  reconstruction and localization debt;
+  if not, close Step 10 as `repackaging obstruction` or
+  `known-family non-coercive against the frozen endpoint`.
+
+- Unexpected findings:
+  the local record is even narrower than the generic tensor-language framing
+  suggests;
+  the strongest source-backed expected success mode is an obstruction memo, not
+  a positive survivor;
+  `full stretching control` survives nowhere on disk as an endpoint-cleared
+  family.
+
+- Computations worth doing later if outside scope:
+  an explicit remote-shell / harmonic-moment cancellation computation from
+  `partial_i partial_j p = R_i R_j(u_i u_j)`;
+  an equivalent-packaging audit across the canonical tensor packages;
+  a reconstruction/localization ledger checking whether any claimed gain leaves
+  a positive-margin smaller coefficient on the complete reconstructed pairing.
+
+---
+
+## Exploration 002
+
+# Exploration 002 Summary
+
+- Goal:
+  screen the surviving Step-10 tensor-family menu across equivalent packagings
+  and decide whether any candidate still earns admission against the frozen full
+  pairing `I_p^far`.
+- What I tried:
+  read the Step-10 goal, the Step-009 freeze and admission-rule reports, the
+  run-006 selected/judgment/attack packet, the Step-001 Tao-gate pressure memo,
+  the far-field pressure obstruction notes, the obstruction-screening notes, and
+  the step-010 receptionist search log; then reduced the live family menu and
+  screened the remaining family across its documented equivalent packagings.
+- Outcome:
+  succeeded.
+- One key takeaway:
+  the live menu collapses to one endpoint-attached `pressure-Hessian /
+  strain-defect` family with `harmonic-moment cancellation` only as a narrow
+  subquestion, and that line still does not survive the repackaging gate because
+  no packaging on disk yields a smaller effective coefficient on the same full
+  pairing `I_p^far`.
+- Packaging screen result:
+  `none survives`.
+- First honest failure:
+  `repackaging obstruction`.
+- Why:
+  the exact pressure relation is only a representation identity unless it
+  changes the coefficient estimate; the eigenframe/alignment variants collapse
+  into local-geometry or criterion language; the restricted-Euler / defect
+  variants collapse into reduced-model or local-defect language; and the
+  harmonic-moment wording counts only if it returns to a smaller coefficient on
+  the full reconstructed pairing, which no local source shows.
+- Leads worth pursuing:
+  only a different branch framing that directly proves remote-shell
